@{PARD}
@{B}Tass Demon Description:@{UB}@{PAR}

These creatures are three feet tall and are covered in an ink black fur from
head to foot. They have pointed ears that gives them exceptional hearing. They
have long front claws with black talons and their feet are padded which reduces
the amount of noise they make when they scurry across the ground (50% move
silently.) Because of their predominatly black colour Tass Demons are very hard
to detect when hiding in shadows (75% chance of success.)@{PAR}

