@{PARD}
@{B}Tass Demon Combat:@{UB}@{PAR}

These little devils will run up attack with both claws and usually scury off. If
both hits are sucessful then the creature has dug into the players skin and the
creature will attempt to bite its opponent. This bite does 1d4 points of damage
and deliever type A poison with it's bite.@{PAR}

@ENDNODE

