@{PARD}
@{B}Tass Demon Habitat/Society:@{UB}@{PAR}

These creatures live in small unorganized packs and attack almost any creature
to obtain food. They usually just visiously attack an oppent until it kills it
or gets killed. Not having the brain power to think of retreating usually. They
make their homes in burrows in the ground.@{PAR}

